# Portfolio Website Project Structure

This is a static portfolio website built with HTML, JavaScript, and Tailwind CSS CDN.

## File Structure
- [index.html](mdc:index.html) - Main homepage
- [about.html](mdc:about.html) - About page
- [projects.html](mdc:projects.html) - Projects showcase
- [services.html](mdc:services.html) - Services offered
- [contact.html](mdc:contact.html) - Contact page and form
- [assets/](mdc:assets/) - Static assets directory
  - [css/](mdc:assets/css/) - Custom CSS files
  - [js/](mdc:assets/js/) - JavaScript files
  - [images/](mdc:assets/images/) - Image assets
- [PRD.md](mdc:PRD.md) - Product Requirements Document
- [todo.md](mdc:todo.md) - Project todo list

## Technology Stack
- HTML5 semantic markup
- Tailwind CSS via CDN
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)
- No build process or frameworks

